OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cold start once again, with
OL,6,Flow cloud for some soon clearing to
OL,7,Fleave another dry and bright day.
OL,8,FWarmer than Thursday with light winds,
OL,9,Fbut feeling cooler near the coast
OL,10,Fwhere some low cloud could linger.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FStaying dry and largely clear
OL,13,Fovernight. Temperatures falling to
OL,14,Fagain give a risk of some rural frost,
OL,15,Fand the potential for some mist and
OL,16,Ffog patches by dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
