OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FAnother dry and fine day
OL,6,Fexpected once early low cloud clears.
OL,7,FSunshine through the afternoon but
OL,8,Flikely cloudier with a fresher breeze
OL,9,Finto the evening. Temperatures
OL,10,Fremaining warm for most.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDry
OL,13,Fwith some hazy sunshine Sunday after
OL,14,Fany early low cloud clears, warm for
OL,15,Fmost. Monday sees a risk of some heavy
OL,16,Fshowers. Drier again into Tuesday but
OL,17,Fturning cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
